===Etymology===
From Slavic ''*zolto-'' (Old Church Slavonic [[злато]]), From Indo-European '''{{Unicode|*ghəl-}}'''. Cognate with Ukrainian '''золото''', Belarusian [[золата]], Bulgarian [[злато]], Serbian [[злато]], Slovenian [[zlato]], Czech [[zlato]], Slovakian [[zlato]], Polish [[złoto]]. The IE root is also the source of Germanic ''*gulþa-'' (English [[gold]]).

